snippet.title: The Incredible Adventures of Van Helsing: Final Cut - Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Prepare for the final challenge - the final instalment of the Van Helsing series is now out on Steam and at the NeocoreGames Store!
Get it now at http://store.steampowered.com/app/400170 or
at http://neocoregames.com/store !

DevBlog: http://www.devblog.neocoregames.com
Facebook: http://www.facebook.com/VanHelsingTheGame
Twitter: https://twitter.com/VanHelsingGame

The Incredible Adventures of Van Helsing is a real-time Action RPG series filled with fierce and demonic battles, memorable characters, and a refreshingly unique story loosely based on Bram Stoker's classic novel Dracula.
